{"tid":1478899,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"200萬人團購國籍","createTime":"2019-08-16T16:42:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T04:42:41.000Z","uid":284147,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d26056c46d96ee52ff44b6f00849c344c5443946","tid":1478899,"uid":284147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:42:33.000Z","msg":"除Bno外（唔掉底97後）， 機會細。<br />\n一邊等， 一邊搵backup plan （呢個係最後bno被否決嘅後備方案）<br />\n<br />\nGroupon原理<br />\n<br />\nStep 1 收集資料present用<br />\n如 200萬人總資產<br />\n每年200萬人可貢獻嘅稅<br />\n職業 技能， 可對國家作出嘅貢獻 建議主打可協助增強法律 金融領域技能<br />\n等等等<br />\n<br />\nStep 2 物色一系列合適國家<br />\n<br />\nStep 3 約不同國家談細節 （呢part 需要律師）<br />\n<br />\nStep 4 收集談回來的方案作公投<br />\n<br />\nEnd"},{"pid":"0399119426ffe354d180c39ed3eedee6e94c26eb","tid":1478899,"uid":82829,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:43:27.000Z","msg":"講到好似真係有200萬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa9817eb7ee8aaecd3cf1f7afe7ffcfb99eeac7","tid":1478899,"uid":108786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:44:44.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"c36d4eef7bde1adf17ebd85db3d4fcc1633c54f5","tid":1478899,"uid":300515,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:45:11.000Z","msg":"唔好傻啦！二百萬一起移民去一度，人哋唔惊啊！"},{"pid":"a8e6ac76761850da5ef00eb8d50f2745c9acdfc4","tid":1478899,"uid":300263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:45:57.000Z","msg":"英美澳紐加都一定唔會理你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最多得同台灣有邦交嘅小國有機會<br />\n但係呢啲小國莫講話200萬人<br />\n多20萬人都未必頂得順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8fec627a72009a8b7fe8e16137410d7ba27d3c7","tid":1478899,"uid":284147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8e6ac76761850da5ef00eb8d50f2745c9acdfc4","tid":1478899,"uid":300263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:45:57.000Z","msg":"英美澳紐加都一定唔會理你<img src=\"/assets